—ЩParchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/from_csv.mdЩ@1fa90e4957d7fdeeef90bf54851807f252c1e6a871c288c73a3df8cfe6a5f5cfҜtitle: from csv‘ЁExamplesЪ5Convert comma-separated data to a table.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> "ColA,ColB
1,2" | from csv
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ # в”Ӯ ColA в”Ӯ ColB в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө
в”Ӯ 0 в”Ӯ    1 в”Ӯ    2 в”Ӯ
в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ


```
Convert comma-separated data to a table, allowing variable number of columns per row.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> "ColA,ColB
1,2
3,4,5
6" | from csv --flexible
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ # в”Ӯ ColA в”Ӯ ColB в”Ӯ column2 в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө
в”Ӯ 0 в”Ӯ    1 в”Ӯ    2 в”Ӯ   вқҺ    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 1 в”Ӯ    3 в”Ӯ    4 в”Ӯ       5 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 2 в”Ӯ    6 в”Ӯ  вқҺ  в”Ӯ   вқҺ    в”Ӯ
в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ


```
Convert comma-separated data to a table, ignoring headers.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> open data.txt | from csv --noheaders


```
Convert semicolon-separated data to a table.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> open data.txt | from csv --separator ';'


```
Convert comma-separated data to a table, ignoring lines starting with '#'.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> open data.txt | from csv --comment '#'


```
Convert comma-separated data to a table, dropping all possible whitespaces around header names and field values.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> open data.txt | from csv --trim all


```
Convert comma-separated data to a table, dropping all possible whitespaces around header names.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> open data.txt | from csv --trim headers


```
Convert comma-separated data to a table, dropping all possible whitespaces around field values.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> open data.txt | from csv --trim fields


```
